name: 29th International Conference on Dental Research & Future Dentistry
content: We are pleased to welcome you to participate in the "29th International Conference on Dental Research & Future Dentistry” which is going to be held May 11-12, 2023 Rome, Italy. • All accepted abstracts will be published in the respective Journals. • Each abstract will receive a DOI provided by Cross Ref. • Exceptional privileges on group registrations. • Opening to organize Workshops/Symposia. • Outstanding Young Researcher Award and Best Poster Award Speaker and abstract pages created in Google on your name would get worldwide.
